With this function you can check the given file to see if it has been synchronised with the Steam Cloud. A return value of <tt>true</tt> means that it is, while <tt>false</tt> means it is not.
The name of the file to check.
The above code will check to see if a file has been stored to the Steam Cloud, and if it has not it will then synchronise it.
